### Auth API

### Register
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "chay",
  "email": "chay@gmail.com",
  "password": "chay123",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Organizations API

### Create Organization
POST http://localhost:8000/api/orgs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Green Earth Foundation",
  "description": "Environmental conservation organization"
}

### Get All Organizations
GET http://localhost:8000/api/orgs

### Get Organization by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/orgs/6932e9319b5491a101841316

### Get Pending Organizations
GET http://localhost:8000/api/orgs/pending

### Approve Organization
POST http://localhost:8000/api/orgs/6932e9319b5491a101841316/approve

### Projects API

### Create Project
POST http://localhost:8000/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Water Initiative",
  "description": "Providing clean water to rural communities",
  "orgId": "6932e9319b5491a101841316",
  "status": "active"
}

### Get All Projects
GET http://localhost:8000/api/projects

### Get Project by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/projects/6932e8d611886926e1aae2c5

### Resources API

### Create Resource
POST http://localhost:8000/api/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "request",
  "title": "Need 100 water filters",
  "description": "Looking for water filtration systems",
  "projectId": "6932e8d611886926e1aae2c5",
  "status": "open"
}

### Get All Resources
GET http://localhost:8000/api/resources

### Contributions API

### Create Contribution
POST http://localhost:8000/api/contributions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "6932e8d611886926e1aae2c5",
  "resourceId": "6932ea429b5491a101841323",
  "description": "I can provide 50 water filters"
}

### Get Contributions by Project ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/projects/6932e8d611886926e1aae2c5/contributions

### Threads API

### Create Thread
POST http://localhost:8000/api/threads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Discussion about water filters",
  "projectId": "6932e8d611886926e1aae2c5"
}

### Create Message in Thread
POST http://localhost:8000/api/threads/6932ea999b5491a10184132b/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "I have experience with water filtration systems. Let me know how I can help."
}

### Get Messages in Thread
GET http://localhost:8000/api/threads/6932ea999b5491a10184132b/messages

